{"tid":1232030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日最少有二百萬人，甚至有二百五十萬人","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:25:17.000Z","uid":98520,"like":154,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"184d269c0189d048de123a0f7cfdd987b68b097c","tid":1232030,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"今日可以開既路都開哂，都仲要行咁耐先到。<br />\n到依家十點幾龍尾仍然味到政總，可想而知今日係幾誇張。<br />\n今日既遊行，反映左我地係可以好團結既。特別印象深刻係行過警察總部，大家一齊屌柒班黑警。香港人繼續加油，記住不撒不散。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjexz2D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjexz2D.png&h=9a43dd84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正皮：香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e882067d7cfaf00e9e188aed006dcc3f11aab3bd","tid":1232030,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2692f8c7123a06ce799bd8fd2c1b5e2f2658705","tid":1232030,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"香港人好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66360fa59479d95dbec29c38f411acf7dd90a86","tid":1232030,"uid":98520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門，等大家知道今日創下左一個超級大壯舉"},{"pid":"9c7174a5859c3e500f278af1e4bb5f8ff51d71ab","tid":1232030,"uid":202077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"頭先有人攞鐳射筆射上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a79f414f925fee39b303820ab01e46064d40b6d","tid":1232030,"uid":98520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c7174a5859c